screen_name: An aggressive and possibility inebriated couple got on the same train as me at Gospel Oak with their dog. They told me they had been visiting elderly relatives and had walked 12k and were now too tired to walk home.

I tested positive for coronavirus on 17th April. With a 2-14 day asymptomatic period, I wonder how much virus was on my bike and bike locks at 19:58 on 11th April when you were angle grinding away..? It’s probably not a good time to be stealing stuff from hospitals right now...
